      "text": "（ⅢXは、I-UNITYで琴乃達と戦った相手だ）\n（決勝でギリギリ、サニピが勝った訳だけど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（IIIX is the group that competed against Moon Tempest in I-UNITY.）\n（In the finals‚ Sunny Peace narrowly won…）",
