      "text": "自分達のマネジメントは自分で出来ますから\n面倒を見ていただく必要はありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But we can manage ourselves‚\nso there's no need for you to take care of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "建前上、マネージャーが必要だとは分かりますけど……\nくれぐれも、余計な口出しはしないようお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand that we need a manager for appearances‚ but…\nPlease refrain from unnecessary interference.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
