      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "いつものアレよ\nすぐに見つけるから、少しくらい待っててちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The usual thing.\nI'll find it right away‚ so please wait a little longer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（……なんで、俺がfranさんなんだ？）\n（それに、様子もなんだかおかしいけど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…Why am I called fran?）\n（And something seems off about her…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "そう言えばfran、{user}さん見た？\nあの人ってば酷いのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ fran‚ have you seen {user}-san?\nThat person is terrible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "今日はサニーピースのレッスン日だって言うから\n練習を偵察出来るかと思ったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They said today is Sunny Peace's rehearsal day‚\nso I thought I could scout their practice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "いざ行ってみたら、もぬけの殻なんだもの\nあの人、私にわざと嘘を教えたんじゃないかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But when I went there‚ it was empty.\nI wonder if that person intentionally lied to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……あの、俺ですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Um‚ it's me actually…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "……失礼しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I apologize.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "……ええと、そこでコンタクトを落としてしまって……\n私、裸眼だとほとんど何も見えないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Um‚ I dropped my contact lenses over there…\nI can hardly see anything without them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "裸眼って……もしかして両目とも落としたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Without your contact lenses?… Did you drop both of them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですけど！　 何か問題でもありますか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yes! Is there a problem with that!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "い、いえ……。そうだ、探すの手伝いましょうか？\n……そこまで何も見えてないんじゃ、危ないでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-No… Um‚ should I help you search for them?\n…It seems dangerous if you can't see anything at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、大丈夫です\n予備のコンタクトも持って来ていますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I'll be fine.\nI have spare contact lenses with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "それと、サニピなら急ぎの打ち合わせに行きましたよ\n……話したいなら、俺から声を掛けてみますけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ Sunny Peace went for an urgent meeting.\n…If you want to talk‚ I can initiate the conversation…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、話したい訳ではないんです\n練習の様子を……その、少しこっそり眺めたいだけで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I don't intend to talk.\nI just wanted to secretly observe their practice for a bit…",
