      "text": "あそこの担当者と直接話が出来るとは……\nさすが、キャリアのあるmihoさんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To have a direct conversation with the person in charge there…\nTruly‚ you're a seasoned professional‚ miho-san.",
